## Conexao:
DB_HOST=db
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DATABASE=local_laravel
DB_USERNAME=local_developer
DB_PASSWORD=secret
DB_CONNECTION=mysql

## Executar contêiner
docker-compose up -d --build

##Bash em seu contêiner:
docker-compose exec app bash

## Instalar Dependencias:
composer install

## Atualizar:
composer update

## Gerar Chave:
php artisan key:generate

### URL Projeto:
http://localhost:8005/


### URL Phpmyadmin:
http://localhost:8081/

### Compilar Assets:
npm install
npm run dev


## Referencia:
https://github.com/iwasherefirst2/laravel-docker
